stories.title: Hussain faces disciplinary action
stories.summary:
Rawalpindi, Oct 30: England captain Nasser Hussain faces disciplinary
action for dissent and damaging equipment in the dressing room

stories.title: Pakistan defeat England by 6 wkts; Wins one day-series
stories.summary:
Rawalpindi, Oct 30: Spin wizard Saqlain Mushtaq bowled Pakistan to
their first one-day series victory over England in 26 years when they
won the third and final one-dayer six wickets at the Pindi Cricket
Stadium here on Monday

stories.title: Pakistan complete series victory with six-wicket win
stories.summary: Pakistan completed a 2-1 series victory over England with this comfortable victory in Rawalpindi
